explains: v. 不赞成，反对；不批准，否决
wordGroup: disapprove of 不赞成；不喜欢

sentences.en: One gets the impression that they disapprove.
sentences.cn: 本人的印象是，他们不赞成。

sentences.en: She wants to be an actress, but her parents disapprove.
sentences.cn: 她想当演员，可是她父母不同意。

sentences.en: "Do you disapprove, nanna?" Justine growled, ready to do battle.
sentences.cn: “外婆，你不赞成吗？”贾斯丁咆哮着，准备要斗争。
